ut an item’s magical properties.\nNotes:\n    The caster must hold or wear the item as it is intended to be used (risking cursed items).\n    Each segment, there is a 15% + 5% per level chance to gain an insight.\n    Each insight is typically either:\n        one magical function (and its command word), or\n        approximate charges (±25%).\n    Exact weapon bonuses are not normally revealed unless the referee chooses.\n    Must be cast within 1 hour/level of the item first coming within 5 feet of the caster, or the caster’s aura “contaminates” the reading.\n    After casting, the caster temporarily loses 8 points of Constitution, regained by resting 1 hour per point.\n    Material component: a pearl worth 100 gp.","link":""},"jump":{"name":"Jump","level":"1","school":"School: Transmutation","range":"Touch","duration":"Special (see below)","aoe":"One creature","components":"V, S, M","ct":"Fast","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"The subject may make one or more great leaps: 30 feet forward, or 10 feet straight up or backward. The leap is nearly straight, without appreciable arc.\nNotes:\nThe spell grants one leap, plus one additional leap for every three levels the caster has above 1st (2nd leap at 4th level, 3rd at 7th, 4th at 10th, etc.).","notes":"The subject may make one or more great leaps: 30 feet forward, or 10 feet straight up or backward. The leap is nearly straight, without appreciable arc.\nNotes:\nThe spell grants one leap, plus one additional leap for every three levels the caster has above 1st (2nd leap at 4th level, 3rd at 7th, 4th at 10th, etc.).","link":""},"light":{"name":"Light","level":"1","school":"School: Transmutation","range":"60 ft.","duration":"1 turn/level","aoe":"20 ft. radius globe","components":"V, S","ct":"Fast","save":"None (special if cast on a creature)","save_type":"","description":"A magical light appears, centered on a point in space, creature, or object. The caster may extinguish it at will. If cast upon magical dark